<!DOCTYPE html
  PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html lang="en" xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">

<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Check Form</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>

<body class="container mt-5" style="display: flex; justify-content: center;">
  <div style="width: 21cm; padding: 1.5cm;">
    <h3 class="text-center pb-3 pt-3">3 DAY NOTICE - PAY RENT OR QUIT</h3>
    <p>
      TO: <%= data.Tenants[0].fname %>
        <%= data.Tenants[0].lname %>, AND ALL OTHERS IN POSSESSION of the premises now held and/or
          occupied by you.
    </p>
    <p>
      The premises herein referred to which are now held and/or occupied by you are located at the
      premises commonly known as: <%= data.address %>, <%= data.cty %>, <%= data.cnty %>, <%=
              data.st %>, <%= data.zip %>.
    </p>
    <p>
      PLEASE TAKE NOTICE that you are justly indebted to the owner of the herein described
      premises; and notice is hereby given that pursuant to the lease and/or rental agreement under
      which you hold possession, there is now due, unpaid and delinquent rent in the total sum
      of <%= data.Particular.Written %> Dollars($<%= data.Particular.Dollars %>).
    </p>
    <p>
      WITHIN THREE (3) DAYS excluding Saturdays, Sundays and other judicial holidays after
      service on you of this notice, you are hereby required to pay the amount of the above std rent
      in full OR quit the subject premises, move out, and deliver up possession to the owner
      and/or his authorized agent.
    </p>
    <p>
      Your payment should be payable to <%= data.Particular.PayToFirst %>
        <%= data.Particular.PayToLast %> and payment shall be delivered at the
          following address <%= data.Particular.address %>, <%= data.Particular.st %>, <%=
                data.Particular.zip %>. Rents are paid to <%= data.Particular.PayToFirst %>
                  <%= data.Particular.PayToLast %> who is usually available on the following days: <%=
                      data.Particular.OpenDays %> weekly. Hours of
                      <%= data.Particular.OpenHours %> daily.
    </p>
    <p>
      PLEASE TAKE FURTHER NOTICE that unless you pay the rent in full OR vacate the premises
      WITHIN THREE (3) DAYS, excluding Saturdays, Sundays, and other judicial holidays, as
      required by this notice, that the undersigned does hereby elect to declare a
      forfeiture of the subject lease and/or rental agreement and will institute legal proceedings for the
      unlawful detainer against you to recover possession of the premises plus court costs, attorney fees
      and PENALTY DAMAGES OF $600.00 due as provided by California law.
    </p>
    <p>
      Pursuant to Section 1785.26 of the California Civil Code, as required by law, you are hereby
      notified that a negative credit report reflecting on your credit record may be submitted to a credit
      reporting agency if you fail to fulfill the terms of your credit obligation.
    </p>
    <p>
      At this time, we have not been informed that your unit is in need of any repairs. We take our
      responsibility as a landlord very seriously. If you believe that items need to be corrected, please
      address those issues in writing and we will immediately inspect and make necessary
      repairs. Of course, if we do not receive any written repair requests, we will assume that there are
      no items that need to be corrected at this time.
    </p>
    <p>
      Personally Served [ ] or Conspicuously Posted [ ] by <%= data.Landlord.fname %>
        <%= data.Landlord.lname %> or Agent AGENT
          NAME
    </p>
    <br>
    <p class="text-end">Signed ____________________________________</p>
    <br>
    <form action="/3day" method="post">
      <input type="number" name='id' value="<%= data.id %>" hidden>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Approve</button>
    </form>
  </div>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>